# Smart AI LMS

Smart AI LMS is an AI-powered Learning Management System built using the MERN Stack and OpenRouter AI. This platform helps students learn smarter with AI assistance, interactive quizzes, and course-based learning.

---

## Project Overview

Smart AI LMS allows users to:

- Create an account and securely log in
- Access course learning content
- Watch course videos
- Generate AI-powered quizzes
- Get help from an AI Assistant
- Learn through an interactive dashboard

---

## Features

- Login & Signup Authentication
- AI Assistant Support
- AI Quiz Generation
- Course Video Learning
- Dashboard System
- Secure Backend API

---

## Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React.js
- Vite
- CSS

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### Database
- MongoDB

### AI Integration
- OpenRouter AI API

